fields.name: OpenStreetMap Data (Generic)
fields.service_description:
OpenStreetMap vector data provided in the 'planet' tables. 

All points, lines, and polygons are three separate tables.
fields.config:
planet_osm_point:
  types:
    - points
  select:
    - name

planet_osm_line:
  type:
    - lines
  select:
    - name

planet_osm_polygon:
  type:
    - polygons
  select:
    - name

fields.name: OpenStreetMap Data (Themes)
fields.service_description:
OpenStreetMap vector data provided in a custom thematic schema. 

Data is grouped into separate tables (e.g. water, roads...).
fields.config:
overpass_query: (relation($bbox);way($bbox);node($bbox););(._;>;);out body;
# gpkg_file: /var/lib/eventkit/osm.gpkg

amenities:
  types:
    - points
    - polygons
  select:
    - amenity
    - name
    - addr:housenumber
    - addr:street
    - building
    - historic
    - information
    - leisure
    - shop
    - tourism
    - office
    - religion
  where: amenity IS NOT NULL

aviation:
  types:
    - points
    - polygons
    - lines
  select:
    - aeroway
    - name
    - surface
    - source
    - building
    - icao
    - iata
    - type
  where: aeroway IS NOT NULL 

places:
  types:
    - points
    - polygons
  select:
    - place
    - name
    - is_in
  where: place IS NOT NULL

buildings:
  types:
    - polygons
  select:
    - building
    - name
    - addr:housenumber
    - addr:street
    - hazard_prone
  where: building IS NOT NULL

natural:
  types:
    - lines
    - polygons
  select:
    - natural
    - name
    - hazard_prone
    - waterway
  where: natural IS NOT NULL

landuse:
  types:
    - polygons
  select:
    - landuse
    - name
  where: landuse IS NOT NULL

roads:
  types:
    - lines
  select:
    - highway
    - barrier
    - ford
    - hazard_prone
    - name
    - traffic_calming
    - tunnel
    - layer
    - bicycle_road
    - bridge
  where: highway IS NOT NULL

rail:
  types:
    - lines
  select:
    - railway
    - name
    - bridge
    - cutting
    - embankment
    - frequency
    - service
    - tracks
    - tunnel
    - usage
    - voltage
    - source
    - operator
    - layer
  where: railway IS NOT NULL

waterways:
  types:
    - lines
  select:
    - waterway
    - name
    - hazard_prone
  where: waterway IS NOT NULL

towers_antennas:
  types:
    - points
  select:
    - man_made
    - name
  where: man_made IN ('antenna','mast','tower')

harbours:
  types:
    - points
  select:
    - harbour
    - name
    - leisure
    - landuse
  where: harbour IS NOT NULL

leisure:
  types:
    - polygons
  select:
    - leisure
    - name
  where:  leisure IS NOT NULL

fields.name: USGS Shaded Relief WMTS
fields.config:
layers:
 - name: imagery
   title: imagery
   sources: [cache]

sources:
  imagery_wmts:
    type: tile
    grid: webmercator
    url: https://basemap.nationalmap.gov/arcgis/rest/services/USGSShadedReliefOnly/MapServer/WMTS?SERVICE=WMTS&REQUEST=GetTile&VERSION=1.0.0&LAYER=USGSShadedReliefOnly&TILEMATRIX=%(z)s&TILEROW=%(y)s&TILECOL=%(x)s&FORMAT=image%%2Fpng

grids:
  webmercator:
    srs: EPSG:3857
    tile_size: [256, 256]
    origin: nw

fields.name: ESRI-Imagery
fields.config:
layer:
  - name: imagery
    title: imagery
    sources: [cache]

sources:
  imagery_arcgis-raster:
    type: arcgis
    grid: webmercator
    req:
      url: http://server.arcgisonline.com/arcgis/rest/services/ESRI_Imagery_World_2D/MapServer
      layers: 
        show: 0

grids:
  webmercator:
    srs: EPSG:3857
    tile_size: [256, 256]
    origin: nw

fields.name: OpenStreetMap Tiles
fields.label: U
fields.service_description:
OpenStreetMap data is rendered into stand-alone raster tiles using a cartography style based on the OSM Standard style.  The only difference is that all features are rendered in English language, as well as the native language, if a the English version is available.  

More information about the copyright of the OSM tiles is found here: https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright

fields.name: Imagery-USGS
fields.label: U
fields.config:
concurrency: 12
max_repeat: 4
formats: 
    gtiff: 
        translate_params: {"creationOptions": ["COMPRESS=JPEG", "PHOTOMETRIC=YCBCR", "TILED=YES", "BIGTIFF=YES"], "bandList": [1,2,3]}

layers:
 - name: imagery
   title: imagery
   sources: [default]

sources:
  default:
    type: wms
    req:
        url: https://basemap.nationalmap.gov:443/arcgis/services/USGSImageryOnly/MapServer/WmsServer
        layers: '0'
    grid: default


caches:
  default:
    grids: [default]
    sources: [default]
    meta_size: [4,4]
    bulk_meta_tiles: true
    request_format: "image/jpeg"
    cache:
        type: geopackage
        filename: "geopackage"
        table_name: 'imagery'

grids:
  default:
    srs: EPSG:4326
    tile_size: [256, 256]
    origin: nw
    res: [0.7031249999999999, 0.35156249999999994, 0.17578124999999997, 0.08789062499999999,
      0.04394531249999999, 0.021972656249999997, 0.010986328124999998, 0.005493164062499999,
      0.0027465820312499996, 0.0013732910156249998, 0.0006866455078124999, 0.00034332275390624995,
      0.00017166137695312497, 8.583068847656249e-05, 4.291534423828124e-05, 2.145767211914062e-05,
      1.072883605957031e-05, 5.364418029785155e-06, 2.6822090148925777e-06, 1.3411045074462889e-06,
      6.705522537231444e-07]

fields.name: OGCAPI-P Imagery Tiles
fields.label: u
fields.config:
ogcapi_process:
  id: "export-eventkit-bundle"
  inputs:
    product: 
      value: "usgs"
    file_format: 
       value: "gpkg" 
  outputs:
     archive_format: 
       format:
         mediaType: "application/zip"
  area:
      name: "geojson"
      type: "geojson"
  output_file_ext: ".gpkg"   
  download_credentials:
    cred_var: EVENTKIT_CRED
cred_var: EVENTKIT_CRED

fields.name: OGCAPI-P DTED0
fields.label: U
fields.config:
ogcapi_process:
  id: "export-tarzip-bundle"
  inputs:
    product: 
      value: "dted0"
    file_format: 
       value: "99" 
  outputs:
     archive_format: 
       format:
         mediaType: "application/zip"
  area:
      name: "wkt"
      type: "wkt"
  output_file_ext: ".dt0"   
  download_credentials:
    cert_info:
      cert_path: /var/lib/eventkit/adhoc/eventkit.stage.gs.mil.pfx
      cert_pass_var: EVENTKIT_CERT_PASS
    cookie: '{"name":"OAMAuthnCookie_websvcs.geo.nga.mil:443","value":"<cookie_value>","domain":"websvcs.geo.nga.mil","path":"/", "secure":"true"}'
cred_var: EVENTKIT_CRED
